ttsdata.text: So you actually went down here before back in 2020 in jewmber?
Yeah roger, I wasn't down here for long before we ended up in that chamber
And now that i'm paying attention, there was a door here along with a torch. Guess it got removed for a while due it's completely left. No biggie, It'll be there again
For what purpose, knowing that you came here kim?
Well, Peter told me about this place before, knowing that an evil and demon looking version of you had been brainwashing you into doing horrible things to me
It was all most the time as if you remember back then
Yeah, The raping. Don't need the reminder
All though i do think that. Yeah, I remember it all. One minute we left there
The next we went back there?
Made a bad decision if you ask me
I honestly have to agree
The chamber thing was sorta good, Jewmber with me being bad and good, other problems sorted out, but um. There's, something i got to ask you about that
All right, sure
Ever since that of last year, Did you happen, to miss anybody there?
Oh? What made you ask?
Well, Marty was there with us in there, and diesel also kinda helped out when he blew our evil selfs up
Isabella, Bobby, That bear. Look at our old friends we've ran into before kim
Huh. I kinda missed them. By the way, I heard that they won't be back due to the voice forge not working anymore and different ones not here, i've heard that from you
Yeah, I did, i was kinda thinking about that some more. Still, Just wonder how they are doing now that we're away from each other
Hey you 2
Oh, Peter, Julie, Paul. What are you 3 doing here?
Nothing. Just dropping to say, this is a pretty much nice corridor this is. All though it is a bit cold in here at, barely times
Time passes by so fast how could it?
